description: Welcome to an exquisite sanctuary in South Boston, quintessential modern living. This bright, spacious residence features two sizable bedrooms and two elegant bathrooms, including a luxurious primary suite. The living and dining area is beautifully framed by large windows with skyline views, 10-foot ceilings, and a cozy gas fireplace. The chic kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample cabinetry and silestone countertops, perfect for culinary adventures. The crown jewel is the 1400 sq ft private roof deck, an urban oasis for entertaining or enjoying serene moments with breathtaking views. Modern amenities include central air, in-unit laundry, and garage parking for ultimate convenience. Nestled in a vibrant community adjacent to Seaport and the new L St Station Redevelopment, this residence isn't just a home—it's a lifestyle. Discover the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and location, offering everything you need for an extraordinary urban living experience
